wen 1.5 13B 经常一连输入几百个换行符，占用推理时间。一开始没有找到解决办法，只好把 max_tokens 设置为和输入文本长度一样（中文译文几乎都比英文短），这样一来最多也就多输出几个换行符，之后在代码里手动 trim 一下就能得到正确结果。后来换了模型就没碰到过这个问题了。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1030,"children":1031},{},[1032],{"type":173,"value":1033},"二是关于请求安全。如果只想让沉浸式翻译浏览器插件调用这个 API，需要手动校验一下 Referer，只要来源是 chrome-extension:xxx 就可以。具体的 extensionId 可以在浏览器插件的管理页面看到。",{"type":167,"tag":220,"props":1035,"children":1037},{"id":1036},"插件设置",[1038],{"type":173,"value":1036},{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1040,"children":1041},{},[1042],{"type":173,"value":1043},"最后是沉浸式翻译插件的设置，首先要在开发者设置里打开 Beta 功能。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1045,"children":1046},{},[1047],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1048,"children":1051},{"alt":1049,"src":1050},"Beta 功能","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403252311878.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1053,"children":1054},{},[1055],{"type":173,"value":1056},"之后，选择“基本设置”，选择自定义接口（⑤），测试一下是否能正常调用（⑥）。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1058,"children":1059},{},[1060],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1061,"children":1064},{"alt":1062,"src":1063},"设置自定义接口","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403252313270.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":168,"props":1066,"children":1068},{"id":1067},"其他可能有用的信息",[1069],{"type":173,"value":1067},{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1071,"children":1072},{},[1073,1075,1080],{"type":173,"value":1074},"有关模型选择的问题。我本地测试了 Qwen 1.5 7B、14B、70B 几种模型，尽管感觉上 70B Q3 的翻译质量好得多，但在 M3 芯片上生成速度太慢，每秒只能输出 17 tokens 约 8 个中文字。",{"type":167,"tag":202,"props":1076,"children":1077},{},[1078],{"type":173,"value":1079},"换 13B 速度够用，但是非常容易出现停止词问题。最后日常翻译我还是选择 7B，速度飞快，还不发热。就是同样的提示词，7B 的返回要加不少戏。",{"type":173,"value":1081},"成文之际又换回了 13B。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1083,"children":1084},{},[1085,1087,1094],{"type":173,"value":1086},"说到提示词。如果你用的不是 Qwen 而是 LLama2 或者不是从高质量中文语料中训练来的模型，那对应的提示词肯定要换。可以参考：",{"type":167,"tag":181,"props":1088,"children":1091},{"href":1089,"rel":1090},"https://docs.anthropic.com/claude/page/polyglot-superpowers",[185],[1092],{"type":173,"value":1093},"Polyglot superpowers",{"type":173,"value":1095},"。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1097,"children":1098},{},[1099,1101,1106],{"type":173,"value":1100},"有关请求速度的设置。由于沉浸式翻译本身自带请求结果缓存，所以无需担心同一个页面的翻译或是重复句子的翻译会多次调用。但本地模型毕竟比不上第三方 API 的速度，如果不想写更多代码（如在本地服务器转发时做更复杂的并发控制），可以单纯地在自定义选项中（⑦）降低沉浸式翻译的每秒请求次数（⑧）。见下图，我的设置是每两秒请求一次（即翻译一个句子）。",{"type":167,"tag":202,"props":1102,"children":1103},{},[1104],{"type":173,"value":1105},"沉浸式翻译能自动断句，所以不用担心单个句子太长。",{"type":173,"value":1107},"成文之际已经把断句关掉了，主观而言，关断句后翻译速度和准确率要更好。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1109,"children":1110},{},[1111],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1112,"children":1115},{"alt":1113,"src":1114},"自定义设置","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403252327002.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1117,"children":1118},{},[1119],{"type":173,"value":1120},"整个链路可替代的选项。本文使用的工具是 LMStudio 本地部署、Qwen1.5、LMStudio Server、NodeJS Proxy、沉浸式翻译插件。在 BiliBili 评论区也见过其他方案，比如有用 Ollama 部署的，用 mT5 的模型翻译的，用全局翻译插件 Bob 替代沉浸式翻译的。总得来说没有见过满分的技术栈。可玩性还很高，如果有时间投入的话。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1122,"children":1123},{},[1124,1126],{"type":173,"value":1125},"最后展示一下翻译效果，分别是 Qwen 1.5 7B q5、14B q6 和 70B q3 的翻译效果。使用的是同一个网页：",{"type":167,"tag":181,"props":1127,"children":1130},{"href":1128,"rel":1129},"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=38590080",[185],[1131],{"type":173,"value":1132},"Can we do better than Git for version control?",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1134,"children":1135},{},[1136],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1137,"children":1140},{"alt":1138,"src":1139},"Qwen 1.5 7B q5","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403260041970.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1142,"children":1143},{},[1144],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1145,"children":1148},{"alt":1146,"src":1147},"Qwen 1.5 13B q6","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403270940123.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1150,"children":1151},{},[1152],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1153,"children":1156},{"alt":1154,"src":1155},"Qwen 1.5 70B q3","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403260024163.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1158,"children":1159},{},[1160],{"type":173,"value":1161},"我在 BiliBili 看到别人说 Q4 程度量化对精度的影响较小，但如果小于 Q4，精度会下降很多。不过从对照组来看，14B q6 的翻译质量确实完胜 14B q2。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":1163,"children":1164},{},[1165,1168],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1166,"children":1167},{"alt":1146,"src":1147},[],{"type":167,"tag":267,"props":1169,"children":1172},{"alt":1170,"src":1171},"Qwen 1.5 13B q2","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202403260038947.png",[],{"type":167,"tag":1174,"props":1175,"children":1176},"style",{},[1177],{"type":173,"value":1178},"html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html.dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-w